ping now.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I mean it was a great run (in Paris) and we lost to two top players today.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999605265665, \"rank\": 3.947332241080815e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great run\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"two top players\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are both top tennis players, we would have had to play very well to win that match and we did not.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top tennis players\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1961}, {\"ngram\": \"that match\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We got into it at the end, but if we found that form earlier we could have caused them problems, but it wasn't to be.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"that form\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We did make the quarters, but if you get through that match you get an opportunity to win a medal.'\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quarters\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"that match\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Hollywood megastar set to perform death-defying stunt during Olympics closing ceremony ArrowMORE:Clare Balding on verge of breaking down while commentating at Olympics ArrowMORE:Andy Murray tennis retirement confirmed after playing his